  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Over 1 billion children live in poverty. Education, which gives them vital knowledge and skills, is key to escaping poverty. But, millions of children don&apos;t have access to education, leaving them at greater risk of an inability to thrive and exploitation. That&apos;s why we&apos;re working to crowdfund $7000 so that the Children at Akplamafu Primary School, Ghana, can thrive. Your contributions will provide meals, laptops for teachers, books, school furniture, art supplies, and even sports jerseys.</narrative>
  </description>
